{"tid":847364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【買不起可以租】台灣ptt網友：租金貴過人工？不可信　個市有古惑","createTime":"2018-10-04T06:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T10:09:21.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57480de5410e59ed966c2abea23eb81abf9fbef2","tid":847364,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1390368304.A.053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1390368304.A.053.html&d=Di3Hi8q1XW4ODRW9VD87TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=53c20764\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1390368304.A.053.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 標題　Re: [新聞] 逆天！香港房價所得比14.9倍<br />\n 時間　Wed Jan 22 13:25:01 2014<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n1. 年輕人當然是買不起房, 別說普通的年輕人, 連當一些高薪職業的專業人士<br />\n　 也抱怨買不起, 月入四萬港幣以上的醫生和律師都覺得負擔很重. 因為他們<br />\n　 月入四五萬, 可是房貸要還的可能就薪水一半, 還有他們要交稅.<br />\n<br />\n2. 至於推文說「買不起就租啊」, 在香港也是不太可行的, 因為香港和臺北不<br />\n　 同的地方是租金也很貴, 租值比率約算是臺北的四倍, 換句話說, 同樣價錢<br />\n　 的樓, 香港的租金是臺北四倍, 買不起的人, 靠租也是半條人命了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152248080852357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10152248080852357&d=Di3Hi8q1XW4ODRW9VD87TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7500bbed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152248080852357</a><br />\n<br />\n香港要增強競爭力, 所有物業減租 75% 就可以做到了, 不需要放棄母語. 你放棄了母語, 你的租還是比別人貴四倍. 我看不出競爭力在哪.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nForest Chui: 即係放棄高地價政策。<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap: 連幾十年的舊樓都可以收成萬銀租, 不是因為高地價政策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336482130.A.ED1.html&d=Di3Hi8q1XW4ODRW9VD87TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2901bdca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n推 obov:台北的房租/房價比　拿出去看真的是房租超便宜<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:精確點來說是房租又比店租便宜非常多<br />\n推 Morisato:台北房子出租20年可能還沒回收一半,房租便宜到爆...<br />\n&rarr; kanako:台北市我有聽過房屋售價可以租同一間房子一百年的<br />\n&rarr; innominate:大台北地區的空房率很高,你不想租出去但別人想<br />\n推 bobju:呵呵,總有房市崩盤的一天,到時就會平衡租金比例. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336286580.A.444.html&d=Di3Hi8q1XW4ODRW9VD87TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=406ed333\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&rarr; innominate:這我不清楚,但租金漲過薪資的話,除非去搶銀行否則怎租?<br />\n&rarr; innominate:而一般的上班族薪資就那樣,你漲租金只是讓你房子沒錢收<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:所以可見台北房價高薪資低 逼房東要降租金配合薪資水準<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:香港就是寧可把屋空著也不會廉租給你.<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:簡單來說, 一個單位 300% 不降價, 好過三個單位 100%.<br />\n&rarr; innominate:香港這樣的情形很妙,也許有空再來研究一下<br />\n&rarr; innominate:理論上能賺一天是一天,因為你不廉租別人也會廉租"},{"pid":"a9104d1537291504f88523ad820e841d5f04ae49","tid":847364,"uid":197196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"我都想知租金貴過人工可以點租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b8b38b3e9811f7c3db4dd1cf6a7e1322653f9b","tid":847364,"uid":179288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9104d1537291504f88523ad820e841d5f04ae49","tid":847364,"uid":197196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"我都想知租金貴過人工可以點租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"夾租囉<br />\n俗稱劏房"},{"pid":"501e9c7811d2269d9930bd5f6d07b17c83dbb04a","tid":847364,"uid":197196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2b8b38b3e9811f7c3db4dd1cf6a7e1322653f9b","tid":847364,"uid":179288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"